{
  "stem": "3012.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only a few pieces of bedding, and a few pans and pots, and-- and just a few dresses or some-- some kind of a clothing we were able to collect and take to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to leave our apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went-- We lived in the same-- same house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In one room, my grandparents and unc-- and the aunts with the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the other room, I-- I-- I was with my parents, and then another aunt, and the child.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Salgotarjan, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In May.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we always tried to keep together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This particular house belonged to a friend of my parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the husband was, I think, already somewhere, I don't know where but-- because the woman was living alone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the husband was-- maybe he was er-- I don't-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because by then, he must have been in his 50s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- she-- she offered us the possi-- the courtesy to stay with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because she was-- she was-- she-- Her house became the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a few days, the gendarmes came in early morning and took away my father, my grandfather, my uncle, and my aunt to a nearby school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they subjected them to horrendous torture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was permitted to take food to my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never had a chance to see the other relatives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I thought I-- I just couldn't believe what I saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In order for them-- for the gendarmerie to get the information under torture from the people where they have hidden certain valuables.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- my family was well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
